          'Freelance and per-task data entry rates range widely. Simple data entry tasks on per-record pricing can pay AED 20 to AED 50 per hour for fast typists. Online platform gigs may pay by project rather than hour. Work-from-home data entry roles at the lower end of the market pay AED 1,500 to AED 3,000 per month for defined hours.',
