          'To work from home on a data entry role legally in the UAE, you need a valid visa. Many remote data entry roles are offered on a freelance or contract basis — if self-employed, you should hold a freelance licence from a UAE free zone. Working without documentation is illegal regardless of whether the work is remote.',
