          'Commission structures also vary widely. Real estate agencies in Dubai offer agents 40% to 60% of the agency\'s commission on a deal. Insurance agents earn 10% to 30% of the premium on new policies. B2B software sales executives earn 5% to 15% of the contract value on closed deals. Some roles include tiered accelerators — earning more per unit once a monthly quota is exceeded.',
